      <article class="eventdetails">
        <main class="wte">
          <p id="wtep">
            BlockchainUNN will organize a 6-week content writing bootcamp for those present in our community, kicking off <b>July 11th, 2023</b>.
            <br><br>
            The bootcamp is aimed at helping participants kickstart their content writing career, and guide them to land their first (paying) role.
            <br><br>
            The bootcamp is divided into three sessions a practical, training and project-based session, looking to cover key areas such as the basics of web3 writing, soft skills required to thrive in the space, and building an attractive portfolio.
          </p>
        </main>
      </article>
      <article class="form" id="formfield">
        <form action="/addCont" method="post">
          <input type="text" name="fullname" id="" placeholder="Fullname" required>
          <input type="email" name="email" id="" placeholder="Email address" required>
          <input type="text" name="phone" id="" placeholder="Phone number" required>
          <div class="dropdown">
            <select name="gender" id="" required>
              <option value=".">Select a Gender</option>
              <option value="Male">Male</option>
              <option value="Female">Female</option>
            </select>
            
          </div>
          <!-- 3rd -->
          <div class="dropdown" >
            <select name="student" required id="">
              <option value=".">Are you a Student</option>
              <option value="Yes">Yes</option>
              <option value="No">No</option>
            </select>
          </div>
           <!-- 4th -->
           <div class="dropdown" >
            <select name="institution" required id="">
              <option value=".">Institution of study</option>
              <option value="UNN/NSUKKA">UNN/Nsukka</option>
              <option value="UNN/UNEC">UNN/UNEC</option>
              <option value="Others">Others</option>
              <option value="I am not a student">I am not a student</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <!-- 5th -->
          <div class="dropdown" >
            <select name="rate" required id="">
              <option value=".">Rate your knowledge of Blockchain Technology</option>
              <option value="0 - First encounter was at the conference">0 - First encounter was at the conference</option>
              <option value="10-30 - Know a thing or two about it">10-30 - Know a thing or two about it</option>
              <option value="40-70 - Pretty knowledgeable about it">40-70 - Pretty knowledgeable about it</option>
              <option value="80-100 - Im very knowledgeable about it">80-100 - Im very knowledgeable about it</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <!-- 6th -->
          <div class="dropdown">
            <select name="hours" id=""  required>
              <option value=".">How many hours in a week can you commit to this bootcamp? </option>
              <option value="10 hours">10 hours</option>
              <option value="15 hours">15 hours</option>
              <option value="20 hours">20 hours</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <input type="submit" value="Register Now" id="reg" name="register" onmouseover="regClicked()" onclick="regClicked()" onmouseleave="regUnclicked()" onsubmit="redirect()">
        </form>
      </article>

      
